casebody.data:
DISCIPLINARY COUNSEL
v.
GREGO 2019-0299 Supreme Court of Ohio. March 14, 2019

DISCIPLINARY CASE

On relator's motion for an order to appear and show cause. Respondent, Lisa Ann Grego, shall show cause by filing with the clerk of this court within ten days a written response as to why respondent should not be held in contempt.
